column3: NSLOCTEXT("[FCA30FAD96AFD89F15C771F15EC59395]", "D99C4CA2457CB676DC003DA694F9D151", "Hmph nothing more than an old book")
NSLOCTEXT("[A9C38D3938E12D4ED0BA872E8934D1B9]", "FE9A3EA945B4D352BF296A83A7B860C5", "Honestly thought this thing was lost when nostradumus took over, bastard destroyed nearly everything I owned. ")

NSLOCTEXT("[A9C38D3938E12D4ED0BA872E8934D1B9]", "249E3C474A943372F96F9C9E5E2B3A03", "You rudly take me from where I can watch everything and the first thing you do is claim I was lost? How fitting for the likes of you. ")
NSLOCTEXT("DT_BookIntro [A9C38D3938E12D4ED0BA872E8934D1B9]", "NewRow_2_Dialogue", "This is new. You were never able to talk before. What is happening here? ")

NSLOCTEXT("DT_BookIntro [A9C38D3938E12D4ED0BA872E8934D1B9]", "3_Dialogue", "I\'ve always been able to speak you ignorant fool! I just chose not to, you were always an annoying child, much like the rest of your pitiful race. You are lucky to even be alive. ")
